OL,3,CPolice in Kansas City investigating
OL,4,Ctheft of England's training equipment
OL,6,FPolice are investigating the theft of
OL,7,Fteam equipment ahead of England's
OL,8,Farrival at their Kansas City base, the
OL,9,FFootball Association has confirmed.
OL,11,FThomas Tuchel's side land in the
OL,12,FMidwest on Saturday afternoon as World
OL,13,FCup preparations go up a notch
OL,14,Ffollowing a warm weather camp in
OL,15,FFlorida.
OL,17,FEngland arrive in Missouri dealing
OL,18,Fwith an unexpected headache, with
OL,19,Fboots and balls reported to have been
OL,20,Fdiscovered stolen ahead of training at
OL,21,FSwope Soccer Village on Saturday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/3
