OL,3,CPolice in Kansas City investigating
OL,4,Ctheft of England's training equipment
OL,6,FThe FA has confirmed that an incident
OL,7,Fhas occurred, but was unable to
OL,8,Fprovide further information given it
OL,9,Fis now a police matter.
OL,11,FThe Kansas City, Missouri Police
OL,12,FDepartment told the Daily Mail: "We
OL,13,Fare investigating a possible theft of
OL,14,Fequipment from a team vehicle that
OL,15,Farrived in Kansas City with items
OL,16,Fmissing this evening. The
OL,17,Finvestigation is ongoing."
OL,19,FEngland are due to train at Swope
OL,20,FSoccer Village for the first time at
OL,21,F5pm local (11pm UK) on Saturday.
