OL,3,CPolice in Kansas City investigating
OL,4,Ctheft of England's training equipment
OL,6,FTuchel's men open their World Cup
OL,7,Fcampaign against Croatia on Wednesday,
OL,8,Fbefore completing Group L against
OL,9,FGhana and Panama.
